messages.content: Everyone can see that the Labour Government has let us down. We need a change in Britain - a real change, not another career MP.

mentions.tacticalSituation: It's a two horse race here in Woking - Labour cannot win. You have two votes at this election - I hope you will also support Cllr Richard Sharpe. He has been a great champion for Knaphill.

leaflet.personalStatement: Please do lend me your support. Thanks and best wishes Rosie Sharpley
leaflet.additionalNotes: Printed by Faze Graphics, Marlborough Road, Woking. Published & promoted by R. McNutt, address on behalf of R. Sharpley (Liberal Democrats) and Richard Sharp (Liberal Democrats) at Sunnybank, Woking, GU22 8SW.
